snippet.title: Dokimon Steam TrailerーSteam Page Launch, Go Wishlist it asap!!
snippet.description:
Hey guys! We finally have a Steam page, go check it out on Steam to wishlist it and get the deets on release date and other such things!

Wishlist it from the steam page!
ENG: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2019300/Dokimon/
日本語: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2019300/Dokimon/?l=japanese


Cheers!
